OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHeatwave shuts schools and 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcuts power in South Sudan  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, All schools have been ordered to close 
OL,6, in South Sudan, as it prepares for a   
OL,7, heatwave in which temperatures could   
OL,8, reach an exceptional 45C (113F).       
OL,10,FAuthorities said children should stay  
OL,11,Findoors and that the extreme weather   
OL,12,Fcould last for at least two weeks.     
OL,14,FDeaths "related to excessive heat" have
OL,15,Falready been reported, officials said  
OL,16,Fon Saturday.                           
OL,18,FResidents in parts of the capital Juba 
OL,19,Fsweltered without electric fans on     
OL,20,FMonday as the heat sparked power cuts. 
